Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.08,0:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.96,0:00:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.27,0:00:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.29,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.33,0:01:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.33,0:01:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.79,0:01:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得妳是幼稚園的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,五代在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.73,0:01:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛剛出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,請妳把這個交給他好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,褓母資格檢定考的問題集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.10,0:01:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代說他想看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代要看這個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼五代會被幼稚園開除呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是他闖了什麼禍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為找到新的褓母,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,這有什麼好隱瞞的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,不管怎麼樣\N請你要好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.57,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,那個…總之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(加油)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#81 愛的執著!\N明日菜果然是學不乖的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經理早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要發表新的人事命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.87,0:02:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣傳部的五代,到前面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.84,0:03:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.61,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要任命你為宣傳部兼任\N福利厚生部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,謝謝經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家也要好好努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.69,0:03:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一,臉上永遠保持笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一,臉上永遠保持笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二,客人的笑容是寶山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊,進來坐,進來坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,老闆,現在超低價\N可以享受極樂氣氛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒唱歌都便宜得要命喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊,進來坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位帥哥,進來坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,現在超低價\N可以享受極樂氣氛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你表現得很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎很有精神嘛,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼突然來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是今天下午來到東京的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說下下星期有個同學會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同學會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.67,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外,我也很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的事我都聽大家說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你想當幼稚園的褓父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是有這個打算啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.05,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是你自己決定的話\N我沒有意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,大家一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,這是奶奶的歡迎會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.73,0:04:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進請進,大老遠的來到這裡\N一定累壞了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢的事你就不必擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想在死之前\N到酒家來喝一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道這種地方\N居然這麼好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我一定會上癮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,別客氣\N喜歡喝什麼儘管叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,奶奶好慷慨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,我喜歡妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是你奶奶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠如此通情達理\N氣度真是非比尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人尊敬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是老人家一時興起而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一時興起,能做到這種地步\N也已經是一流的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好對待你奶奶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,我們來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好好,我知道了,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要玩什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩什麼好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎馬打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來接妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.97,0:06:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,這不是五代的奶奶嗎\N妳還是這麼有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說…你來接我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭,今天要上網球課啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從上次掃墓之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐的爸媽都非常喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是恭喜你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去準備一下吧\N他都特地來接妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是太天真了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,不管她爸媽怎麼喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,最重要的是管理員的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把私奔的旅費都籌好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們得私奔不可?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣工作不穩定的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐的爸媽\N不可能允許你們在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管他什麼父母的意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是想私奔是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的親友強力反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於來到北國的小鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過著窮困潦倒的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.16,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要想像成這麼灰暗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在聊什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,妳先上車去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你能夠獨當一面之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會先將她的心融化的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,快點啊,快點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連奶奶都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹那傢伙會使出什麼手段?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.02,0:08:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千圓就行了,我最近很閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,五百圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.01,0:09:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢,下星期天怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還問我有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得去拜訪一下\N三鷹的爸媽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請他們好好照顧我們女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有答應他們結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要為這種無聊的事\N打電話到公司來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.33,0:09:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道,三鷹為了響子\N拒絕了相親的婚事耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.74,0:09:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎麼說\N我一定要讓他們兩人結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,關於報價單的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.92,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂喂喂,這份資料各印三份\N-這些人未免太假了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.39,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的,明天一定盡早處理\N好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳打得好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.74,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候玩鍵子板,從來沒輸過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的讓我等了很久啊\N音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.36,0:10:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,護城河已經被我\N填得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次絕對不讓妳逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教練,教練我在叫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有新人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是三鷹教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小女子不才,還請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛嚇成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼來了?明日菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的婚事明明已經吹了\N已經吹了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.31,0:12:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐,請跟我來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請這邊走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是那個帶狗狗的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.83,0:12:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的,我無法和妳結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點,明日菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候\N妳不是已經明白了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說,你並不討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.27,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你說你討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能就自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪我覺得很眼熟\N她是相親照片上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是教練相親的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?那個女孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.03,0:13:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有這個女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.13,0:13:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情越來越有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果會怎麼樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.01,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來她就是\N三鷹教練相親的對象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.58,0:13:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是三鷹教練說他們分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.19,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然跑到網球場來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來她真的很喜歡教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐,我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來參加網球教室的事\N妳爸媽知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道,而且他們都贊成我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.18,0:14:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說去了解一下\N未來夫婿的職業是一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.85,0:14:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我去打個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.76,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,教練竟然溜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是要宣戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.64,0:14:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果叫她跟三鷹先生分手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.28,0:14:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會很生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得說說話才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得說說話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.36,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,妳的狗狗們都還好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託妳的福,牠們都很平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳家的惣一郎好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然記得惣一郎的名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.41,0:15:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗的名字\N我只要聽過一次就不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人談得蠻愉快的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還問我什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是明日菜的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.17,0:15:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樁婚事應該已經吹了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹了?你在胡說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.51,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很清楚地\N拒絕了明日菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?你一個人在笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我會去九条家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她爸媽把事情講清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿片,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溼紙巾,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶粉也還夠\N看來今天不用出去買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學科考試在九月啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像蠻困難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.49,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前前後後要花一年的時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,太好了,你在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊,這麼早就來上班了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,太郎,快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎好喜歡部長哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.11,0:17:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直催我快點來工作\N真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-對不對?\N-對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長要是能當你的爸爸\N不知道有多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.89,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是愛說笑\N霞姊,妳有老公吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.80,0:17:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在找新的老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.34,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,你很喜歡小孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是蠻喜歡小孩的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,太郎和花子\N拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司內法規第三條\N你說說看是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司內禁止戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.88,0:18:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你誤會了啦,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.55,0:18:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一出事的話,你會被開除喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲,阿瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.61,0:18:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,你怎麼來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的決心是不會改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個聲音是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬,怎麼這麼晚才來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也終於想定下來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來,我肩膀的重擔\N就能卸下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你設計的是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早看穿你的個性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢破壞這種溫馨的氣氛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樁婚事,我斷然拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明…明日菜小姐,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我死吧,如果不能跟你結婚\N乾脆讓我死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.17,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到明日菜這麼愛三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好專情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.82,0:20:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,健康是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.56,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種場合,我果然還是說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?\N他還跟相親的對象在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.54,0:20:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道三鷹一直都在說謊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起來很為難的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.62,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來才是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹好像被逼到走投無路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.56,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N管理員也不能悠閒地打掃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.69,0:21:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定參加明年的\N褓母資格檢定考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.00,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳也…很多事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.11,0:22:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,褓父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然一臉天真的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.12,0:22:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底知不知道\N自己現在處於什麼立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來,過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.15,0:22:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能依靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.29,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.62,0:22:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我會很為難…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.40,0:22:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.96,0:22:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司內法規第三條!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.47,0:22:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.27,0:22:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.94,0:23:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,店裡打烊了之後\N看看這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.23,0:23:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎和花子,請你多多照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.27,0:23:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小霞那傢伙跟客人跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.78,0:23:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.51,0:23:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.53,0:23:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,她在哭耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.39,0:23:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點把她的媽媽找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.73,0:23:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連宴會都不能開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.40,0:24:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找過了,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.90,0:24:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N『滿分爸爸!五代的育兒故事』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.81,0:24:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被逃掉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.05,0:24:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.25,0:24:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.26,0:24:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.50,0:24:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.71,0:24:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.31,0:24:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
